	"Wait Master, let me get that." Minnie flutters over with her wings to me and grabs my plate to clean it. "Hey, I can help you out back here when it comes to cleaning if you'd like, I figured I'd take a few days to get situated before I started writing." Minnie cutely giggles at what I say. "Master, that's awfully generous of you, I'd love it if you'd help me clean."
