	"Jeez Master Adrian, ya look like ya just saw yer ghost or somethin, whatsamatter~?" She said facetiously. After taking a few seconds to calm down at the sight of the spider-maid, I explained to her how I was going through the empty bedrooms because it made me wonder where the ladies' sleeping quarters were.
